<nav class='breadcrumb m4 show-lg'>Watch&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="breadcrumb__link" href="/watch/topics" rel=" up">Topics</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;</nav>

<h1 class='h1 h1--alt m2'>
Happiness
</h1>

</div>

<div class='row'>
<div class='col col-lg-sidebarred'>
<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='p2'>
<p>We all want to be happy. But how, exactly, do you go about it? The answers in these TED Talks on happiness -- from psychologists, journalists and monks -- may surprise you.</p>

</div>



<!-- PB:B: dynamic -->
<div class='section section--minor'>
