</a></div>


<!-- PB:B: copy --><div class='clearfix'>
<figure class='Figure' style=''>
<a href="http://www.npr.org/programs/ted-radio-hour/267185371/simply-happy" target="_blank"><img alt='TRH: Happiness' class='Figure__image' src='//pb-assets.tedcdn.com/system/baubles/files/000/000/970/original/topics_TRH_happiness.jpg?1401472709'>
</a></figure>
<div class='copy text-left'>
<h4 class="h7 m5">Episode: Simply Happy</h4>

<p>We all want to find happiness, but it seems elusive. Can we learn more about happiness through science? Or are there simpler ways to achieve it? <a href="http://www.npr.org/programs/ted-radio-hour/267185371/simply-happy"><strong>Listen now</strong></a></p>

